Load in BioStore capacity Excel file from Karen Beeri

readKBExcel.Rd

Load in BioStore capacity Excel file from Karen Beeri

Usage

readKBExcel(x = "calculator_for_Suman.xlsx")

Arguments

x

Exact name of the file

Value

A clean tibble of the Excel file for further manipulation

Examples

readKBExcel()
